channel.title: Cant play any rsps! Please help!
channel.description:
I cant play any rsps, it says "Error connecting to server" for evry rsps what i try. I tried:
[ul][li]Emps-Scape[/li] [li]Pwnxile[/li] [li]Some RS-PS servers[/li][/ul]
None worked but they are online. I can only play servers over hamachi. It worked like 1 year ago. Evrything was okay. Ive tried with different computers, reinstalled windows many times still nothing. Btw this happend to all in the network not only to me. Wtf is going on????
